<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.9.11">
<l>viṭalil cakkarat taṇṇalai mēval</l>
<l>viṭalil vaṇkuru kūrccaṭa kōpaṉcol</l>
<l>keṭali lāyirat tuḷḷivai pattum</l>
<l>keṭalil vīṭucey yuṅkiḷar vārkkē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The ten in the indestructable thousand</l>
<l>among the words of Caṭakōpaṉ from liberal Kurukūr that do not let go</l>
<l>of being attached to the majesty with the flawless discus</l>
<l>make indestructable liberation to those who utter [them].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
